Package: gam2formula
Title: Formulas from splines fitted in 'mgcv'
Version: 0.2.6
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Paul", family = "Bach",
         email = "paul.bach@iqtig.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person(given = "Stefan", family = "Gehrig",
         email = "stefan.gehrig@iqtig.org", role = c("aut")))
Description: Converts spline smooths from generalized additive models
    fitted with 'mgcv' into closed-form algebraic formulas that can be
    printed, exported to 'LaTeX', and predicted from.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
